  "sections": {
    "summary": {
      "name": "Summary",
      "columns": 1,
      "separateLinks": true,
      "visible": true,
      "id": "summary",
      "content": "<p><strong>CTO and Technical Lead with over 12 years of experience</strong>, whose professional journey highlights a strong <strong>propensity for experimentation and continuous learning</strong>. Starting from a solid foundation as a Full Stack Developer, <strong>expertise has been developed in software architecture and engineering</strong>, mastering both frontend and backend design patterns.</p><p>This aptitude for change is demonstrated by the <strong>recent adoption of emerging technologies</strong>: the <strong>development of AI agents</strong> for automation has been led, and personal projects in the <strong>Web3 space</strong>, such as wallets and smart accounts, have been delivered. Technical leadership and architectural vision are combined with the ability to quickly assimilate and apply new paradigms.</p>"
    },
