          "position": "Chief Technology Officer (CTO)",
          "location": "Verona",
          "date": "Since January 2024",
          "summary": "<p>Defined the <strong>software architecture</strong> and drove company-wide technological choices, ensuring alignment with business goals. Responsibilities included <strong>managing complex multi-tenant systems, addressing scalability challenges, and implementing robust Access Control Lists (ACLs)</strong>. Directed and coordinated development teams, optimizing workflows. Implemented <strong>advanced, secure authentication systems</strong> and developed <strong>AI agents</strong> for process automation and applied artificial intelligence. The infrastructure leveraged <strong>Docker</strong> and scalable <strong>AWS services</strong>.</p>",
          "url": {
            "label": "",
            "href": "https://4hse.com"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "etime",
          "visible": true,
          "company": "E-Time Software House",
          "position": "Full Stack Developer",
          "location": "Verona",
          "date": "2015 - 2023",
          "summary": "<p><strong>Full-Stack Technology Consulting</strong> provided to clients in highly regulated and innovative sectors, including <strong>Banking, Insurance</strong>, and online learning platforms (<strong>LMS</strong>, e.g., Docebo). The work was conducted using <strong>Scrum/Agile methodologies</strong> and covered the entire project lifecycle, from initial strategic consulting and design to the development and deployment of custom web solutions.</p>",
          "url": {
            "label": "",
            "href": "https://e-time.it"
          }
        },
