          "date": "2025",
          "summary": "<p><strong>Non-custodial Smart Wallet and programmable Smart Account</strong> for the Koinos blockchain. It ensures immediate and <strong>barrierless access</strong> through innovative authentication leveraging <strong>OpenID and Passkeys</strong> standards. Designed as an <strong>extensible Smart Account</strong> for future modular features.</p>",
