          "description": "Modular Smart Account Framework",
          "date": "2024",
          "summary": "<p><strong>Opensource framework that enables modular Smart Accounts</strong> on the Koinos blockchain (inspired by ERC-7579). Its goal is to <strong>remove barriers to blockchain adoption</strong> by allowing universal onboarding and offering customizable account extensions.</p>",
